plotly

Some Plots!

library(tidyverse)
library(p8105.datasets)

library(plotly)
data("rest_inspec")

ny_rest = 
  rest_inspec %>%
  select(boro, cuisine_description, dba, score, violation_code, zipcode, grade) %>%
  filter(boro %in% c("BRONX", "BROOKLYN", "MANHATTAN", "QUEENS", "STATEN ISLAND")) %>%
  drop_na(grade)

Scatterplot

ny_rest %>%
  filter(grade %in% c("A", "B", "C")) %>%
  plot_ly(
    x = ~zipcode, y = ~score, color = ~grade, type = "scatter", mode = "markers"
  )
## Warning: Ignoring 3 observations

Boxplot

ny_rest %>%
  filter(boro == "MANHATTAN",
         grade %in% c("A", "B", "C")) %>%
  plot_ly(y = ~score, color = ~grade, type = "box")

Bar chart

ny_rest %>% 
  count(boro, violation_code, name = "count") %>%
  mutate(violation_code = fct_reorder(violation_code, count)) %>%
  plot_ly(x = ~violation_code, y = ~count, color = ~boro, type = "bar")
## Warning: Ignoring 5 observations
